cs.CV, cs.GR, cs.RO, cs.AI, cs.LG

This paper deals with computer vision and graphics, specifically the alignment of 2D images with 3D models. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves robotics (cs.RO) as it discusses the use of 3D models for object recognition and retrieval. The use of convolutional neural networks (CNNs) for surface normal prediction suggests that the paper may also fall under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). Finally, the paper involves the use of CAD models, which suggests that it may also fall under cs.GR (Computer Graphics).
